{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "4.080", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrter Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "4.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "5.240", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "5.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "6.600", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "7.800", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe G\u00e4ste! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "7.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.160", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist eine uralte Binsenweisheit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.280", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ein nahezu durchaus uraltes Ph\u00e4nomen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "17.240", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "selbst wenn es die AfD nicht wahrhaben will\u00a0\u2013: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "17.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "18.920", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Gerade in schweren Zeiten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "18.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "28.000", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in Zeiten sozialer Spannungen und sozialer Umbr\u00fcche werden religi\u00f6se Minderheiten gerne zum Opfer von Verfolgung und Pogromen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "28.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "33.920", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das sollte gerade uns aus unserer deutschen Geschichte heraus kein unbekanntes Ph\u00e4nomen sein."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "33.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "35.320", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch die Rohingya, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "35.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "38.960", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "eine muslimische Minderheit im buddhistisch gepr\u00e4gten Myanmar, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "38.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "42.400", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "werden seit Jahrzehnten systematisch ausgegrenzt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "42.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "44.000", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "verfolgt und ermordet. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "44.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "46.200", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das sollten auch Sie zur Kenntnis nehmen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "46.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "51.320", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Denn sie besitzen weder die Staatsangeh\u00f6rigkeit noch andere politische Rechte. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "51.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "52.400", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deren Leid\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "52.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "56.080", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "daran machen Sie sich durch Ihre \u00c4u\u00dferungen mitschuldig\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "56.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "59.800", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist unermesslich und betrifft vor allem Frauen und Kinder. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "59.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "61.440", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das haben wir hier schon geh\u00f6rt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "61.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "62.080", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ja, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "62.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "65.160", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dabei sind Regierung und Milit\u00e4r die Drahtzieher, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "65.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "66.880", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "oder sie schauen einfach weg, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "66.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "69.640", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "statt die Situation richtig zu analysieren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "69.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "76.240", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In der Tat ist auch schon das Schweigen der Friedensnobelpreistr\u00e4gerin Aung San Suu Kyi kritisiert worden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "76.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "77.600", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "v\u00f6llig zu Recht."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "77.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "83.760", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Was aber ist der Grund f\u00fcr diese Gewaltexzesse gegen die Rohingya? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "83.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "86.320", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wer profitiert eigentlich von deren Leid, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "86.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "87.600", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "von deren Elend? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "87.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "89.000", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In Myanmar, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "89.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "92.520", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in einem Land mit weit \u00fcber 100\u00a0Volksgruppen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "92.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "96.280", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sind ethnische Konflikte und Spannungen leider an der Tagesordnung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "96.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "99.400", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Was aber fast alle Volksgruppen dort verbindet, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "99.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "101.240", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist ihr buddhistischer Glaube."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "101.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "104.320", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Rohingya wiederum sind Muslime: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "104.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "106.920", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie glauben und sie beten anders. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "106.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "113.920", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie sehen anders aus und passen deshalb in den Augen vieler buddhistischer Mitmenschen nicht zur Gesellschaft."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "113.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "116.120", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kommt Ihnen das irgendwie bekannt vor? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "116.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "117.120", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mir schon."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "117.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "119.040", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie werden verabscheut, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "119.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "120.840", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "gehasst und misshandelt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "120.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "126.720", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie sind geradezu S\u00fcndenb\u00f6cke einer von Gewalt und Elend gekennzeichneten Gesellschaft. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "126.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "127.160", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ja, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "127.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "131.080", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wir sprechen in der Tat bereits von ethnischen S\u00e4uberungen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "131.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "132.800", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u2013\u00a0Vielleicht h\u00f6ren Sie einfach einmal zu. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "132.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "136.120", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie k\u00f6nnten noch eine ganze Menge an Humanit\u00e4t lernen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "136.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "136.760", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ja, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "136.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "139.840", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das mag uns gelegentlich \u00fcberraschen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "139.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "145.640", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil wir im Westen eigentlich das Bild von einem sehr friedvollen Buddhismus haben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "145.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "148.960", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dass hier die Buddhisten die unterdr\u00fcckende Mehrheit sind, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "148.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "150.480", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "hat in der Tat etwas, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "150.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "152.760", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was uns vielleicht \u00fcberrascht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "152.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "154.480", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber es zeigt doch eines: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "154.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "159.320", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nicht die Religion ist der Grund f\u00fcr dieses V\u00f6lkermorden; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "159.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "161.960", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Ursachen liegen offensichtlich viel tiefer. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "161.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "164.440", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Solange Religion Privatsache ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "164.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "166.200", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist sie eigentlich nie ein Problem. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "166.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "169.280", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie wird dann zum Problem und zum Konfliktherd, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "169.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "173.080", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn sie durch Macht und Interessen instrumentalisiert wird, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "173.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "175.920", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und das machen Sie t\u00e4glich zur Tagesordnung."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "175.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "180.040", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Genau das passiert aber auch in Myanmar mit den Rohingya. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "180.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "180.680", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deshalb, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "180.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "183.320", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "liebe Staatsministerin Frau M\u00fcntefering, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "183.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "184.760", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ersuchen wir Sie auch, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "184.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "185.680", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "alles zu tun, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "185.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "188.120", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um diesen V\u00f6lkermord zu stoppen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "188.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "191.360", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Lassen Sie uns Mitverantwortung an dieser Stelle \u00fcbernehmen,"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "191.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "195.320", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "damit die Regierung in Myanmar davon \u00fcberzeugt werden kann, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "195.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "198.960", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Rohingya alle ihre b\u00fcrgerlichen Rechte brauchen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "198.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "202.800", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass ihnen auch ihre politischen Rechte zuerkannt werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "202.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "204.400", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass es ihnen m\u00f6glich wird, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "204.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "208.040", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sicher und freiwillig aus Bangladesch zur\u00fcckzukehren\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "208.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "209.480", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wir haben es schon geh\u00f6rt\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "209.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "212.400", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Menschenrechtsverletzungen gestoppt werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "212.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "217.440", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Opfer entsch\u00e4digt werden k\u00f6nnen und dass wir auch flankierend eingreifen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "217.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "220.080", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um humanit\u00e4re Hilfe zu leisten."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "220.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "223.520", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir ersuchen Sie weiterhin, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "223.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "226.320", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Vereinten Nationen anzurufen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "226.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "227.720", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "auch das haben wir geh\u00f6rt\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "227.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "230.920", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "damit die Menschenrechtsverletzungen nicht nur aufh\u00f6ren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "230.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "232.160", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "unterbleiben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "232.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "235.440", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern auch verfolgt und geahndet werden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "235.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "236.200", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ja, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "236.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "237.720", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "237.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "239.320", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wir sind der Auffassung\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "239.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "241.800", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "au\u00dfer offensichtlich die AfD\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "241.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "247.440", 
   "id": "s000087", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Rohingya in Myanmar oder in Bangladesch genug gelitten haben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "247.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "248.080", 
   "id": "s000088", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie haben\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "248.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "251.400", 
   "id": "s000089", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nehmen Sie dies doch bitte ausdr\u00fccklich zur Kenntnis!\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "251.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "252.800", 
   "id": "s000090", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ein Recht auf W\u00fcrde, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "252.800", 
   "children": [], 
